blockchainMetadata.questionHeader: Will ETH next 5 min candle be Green: Price at 9:35 PM higher or equal to 9:30 PM UTC, Jan 30
blockchainMetadata.questionDescription:

 NO: This market will resolve to NO if ETH close price is strictly below open price for 5 min candle starting at 9:30 PM UTC on Jan 30.
            

 Only open and close prices of the same candle, which starts at 9:30 PM UTC, are considered for settlement.
